OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWaitrose offers police free
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcoffees to deter thieves   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Waitrose and John Lewis are offering   
OL,6, free hot drinks to on-duty police      
OL,7, officers in a bid to deter shoplifters.
OL,9,FJohn Lewis Partnership, which owns both
OL,10,Fbrands, has written to the Police      
OL,11,FFederation to say officers can make the
OL,12,Fmost of the offer - as long as they    
OL,13,Fbring a reusable cup.                  
OL,15,FIts head of security said that even    
OL,16,Fjust having a police car parked outside
OL,17,Fmight deter would-be thieves.          
OL,19,FIt comes as other shops have reported  
OL,20,Fsoaring levels of retail crime.        
